# Patterns (regex) for URLs lychee should skip in the docs link check.
#
# Codecov badge SVG: a dynamically generated status image whose badge service
# intermittently returns 504 Gateway Timeout, flaking the link check for reasons
# unrelated to any change in this repo. The badge renders fine in the README and
# is not a documentation link worth gating CI on. The Codecov *project* link
# (codecov.io/gh/dknauss/Sudo) is still checked.
codecov\.io/gh/dknauss/Sudo/graph/badge\.svg
